# ============================================================================
# COMMON SEARCH PATTERNS
# ============================================================================

search-patterns:
  "How do I implement X?":
    - Path 1: Check docs/reference/ for API signatures + examples
    - Path 2: Check docs/patterns/ for implementation patterns
    - Path 3: Check docs/architecture/ for system design

  "Why did we choose X?":
    - Path 1: Check docs/architecture/tech-stack.md
    - Path 2: Check docs/architecture/ for design decisions

  "What's the API for X?":
    - Path 1: Check docs/reference/ for function signatures
    - Path 2: Check docs/architecture/ for API specification

